title: Chef Peter Fontanez
text:
FOOD , NEWS 
Peter Fontanez grew up in NYC and graduated High School in Tampa, Florida. He took an entry level job upon graduating High School and has worked his way up the corporate kitchen ladder to the rank of Executive Sous Chef of the Dena’ Ina Convention Center in Anchorage, Alaska. Peter Fontanez is on the far right.
